{"title":"水下红太阳","authors":["秦天祥"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"水下红太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士　秦天祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一支脱弦的箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潜艇离开了军港。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们载负着人民的期望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜战斗在大海的心脏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水下看不到太阳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的象照得全舱亮堂堂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚这里看不到星光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象北极星指示着我们的航向！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们抬头看到这张象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下添力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风再狂，浪再险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无法撼动我们钢铁的脊梁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们俯首翻开这本书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道金光眼前亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲反帝的战鼓越擂越响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心中的火能煮沸大海洋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是我们心中的红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在海底筑起一道屏障；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌舰胆敢来侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就把它彻底埋葬！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}